</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-32_ pf-text-1">In the UK alone, head injuries account for approximately 1.4 million A&amp;E attendances each year.





</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-34_ pf-text-1">Falls are the leading cause of head injuries, followed by motor vehicle accidents, sports-related incidents, and assaults.






